ote><br />\n講到咁易，咁唔考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82e8e38082975f68a8f7123a861b5388ffd243ef","tid":368191,"uid":124899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:44:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>公開考試差幾分就一個級。<br />\n有乜精唔精英。<br />\n你同其他大學生差既咁多科合計可以都無三十分(以每科一百分黎計)</blockquote><br />\n講到咁易，咁唔考多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n十年前試過喇<br />\n連續兩年考同一科<br />\n後果年重要無乜溫<br />\n<br />\n第一年得D仔<br />\n第二年有個B<br />\n<br />\n我講緊果陣既A-LEVEL<br />\n<br />\n根本公開試好多時都係運氣黎。唔好睇到自己咁高喇"},{"pid":"078bd61dec60f60ccac8343c52d5c85ab021f4cd","tid":368191,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:45:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>公開考試差幾分就一個級。<br />\n有乜精唔精英。<br />\n你同其他大學生差既咁多科合計可以都無三十分(以每科一百分黎計)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又唔係咁講<br />\n只係三大有d科太廢太易入姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得公開試係分到一個人精唔精英<br />\n你考一次30分就入神科同考兩次先2幾分入普通科已經係智商上嘅分別"},{"pid":"d03cdb8bc48855d0ba953c10ef0bfa4ecb679ada","tid":368191,"uid":135692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:46:50.000Z","msg":"Hku science 唔算精英<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"162bce1a43ef8b067320153c06cd594bcec129d8","tid":368191,"uid":77180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:48:08.000Z","msg":"只可以話三大入面有好多都平庸<br />\n但公開試勁嗰班本質上已經係精英"},{"pid":"20c6ac9993739acc86f98800bb4278e13f7409d2","tid":368191,"uid":42764,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T14:59:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只可以話三大入面有好多都平庸<br />\n但公開試勁嗰班本質上已經係精英</blockquote><br />\n咁入唔到三大點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n八大都入唔到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b77b44888fcca65347b6be6961525b4369fef8","tid":368191,"